Notes

Filtring is a re-named Galarian Weezing. In Pokemon Voyager, the Galar region was destroyed centuries ago, but some of its regional variants remain.

Evolution
Pokedex

Egg group - AMORPHOUS

Getting up close to a Koffing will give you a chance to observe, through its thin skin, the toxic gases swirling inside. It blows up at the slightest stimulation.
By diluting its toxic gases with a special process, the highest grade of perfume can be extracted. To Filtring, gases emanating from garbage are the ultimate feast.
Weezing alternately shrinks and inflates its twin bodies to mix together toxic gases inside. The longer they mix, the more powerful the toxins become.
